⚠️  HQ HARNESS - MISSING STATE FILES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

.harness/features.json not found!

Before implementing, ensure harness files exist:
  1. .harness/features.json → Feature list with passes: true/false
  2. .harness/progress.txt  → Session history

Read: anthropic.com/engineering/effective-harnesses-for-long-running-agents

