Follow the harness workflow:

  1. READ .harness/progress.txt    → Understand session history
  2. READ .harness/features.json   → Find next feature (passes: false)
  3. IMPLEMENT one feature
  4. TEST visually (bun tauri dev + Playwright MCP)
  5. COMMIT after passing
  6. UPDATE .harness/progress.txt

CRITICAL RULES:
  ✗ Never guess versions - use bun add / cargo add
  ✗ Never mark UI complete without screenshot verification
  ✓ Always check current date (not training year)
  ✓ One feature at a time, production-ready before stopping

